==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wanting
<hw>Want"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Absent; lacking; missing; also,
deficient; destitute; needy; <as>as, one of the twelve is
<ex>wanting</ex>; I shall not be <ex>wanting</ex> in
exertion</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 1626 -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wantless</ent>⟦br⟧
